Forgive me for the eBay links - but I will sort them for you and have them organized by Grade and TPG company. The quantity I have is what has prevented me from listing here more. I would love for them to go to Net54ers! If you are looking for a specific player or team, just add the respective keyword after what is in the search box on the site. 
⚾⚾⚾⚾
Whatever price you see, know that you can take 15% off everything if paid through PayPal FF/Venmo/Zelle. I will cover all shipping costs. 
⚾⚾⚾⚾

If you don't feel like doing the math, just give me a list and I can send you a quote. Offers beyond 15% are always welcome, and I will always respond. I am not an automatic counterofferer if that makes sense. :D It's very possible I might have a few that have been on there for a bit, and now have prices that are outdated. Just reach out to ask about one or multiple cards and I will definitely try to work with you.
